            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "After exploring a field and leaving, you will see <CLGR>Gathering Results<CLNR>."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "The star rating represents how much of the area you explored, and increases by gathering and fighting battles."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "If you press <IM04> with 4 or more stars, you can continue exploring the same field. *This will consume LP."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Exploring the same field lets you gather better materials, but the enemies will get stronger too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "If your party is wiped out, you will lose the items that you gathered in the field, so be very careful."
        }
    ]
}